📧 Sync Inbox dari luar (Cron)

POST /api/email/sync-inbox dengan header:
  Authorization: Bearer <SYNC_INBOX_CRON_SECRET>
  atau x-api-key: <SYNC_INBOX_CRON_SECRET>

Set env: SYNC_INBOX_CRON_SECRET=your-secret-string

Contoh cron (setiap 5 menit):
  curl -X POST https://yoursite.com/api/email/sync-inbox \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer your-secret-string"